<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><Regulation lims:pit-date="2006-03-22" lims:lastAmendedDate="2006-03-22" lims:current-date="2025-07-24" lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:fid="1000947" lims:id="1000947" gazette-part="II" regulation-type="SOR" xml:lang="en" xmlns:lims="http://justice.gc.ca/lims"><Identification lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:fid="1000948" lims:id="1000948"><InstrumentNumber>SOR/96-446</InstrumentNumber><RegistrationDate><Date><YYYY>1996</YYYY><MM>9</MM><DD>17</DD></Date></RegistrationDate><ConsolidationDate lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22"><Date><YYYY>2025</YYYY><MM>7</MM><DD>25</DD></Date></ConsolidationDate><EnablingAuthority lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:fid="1000950" lims:id="1000950"><XRefExternal reference-type="act" link="M-10.01">MOTOR VEHICLE SAFETY ACT</XRefExternal></EnablingAuthority><LongTitle lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:fid="1000951" lims:id="1000951">Nova BUS Corporation Exemption Order</LongTitle><RegulationMakerOrder><RegulationMaker>P.C.</RegulationMaker><OrderNumber>1996-1455</OrderNumber><Date><YYYY> 1996</YYYY><MM>9</MM><DD>17</DD></Date></RegulationMakerOrder></Identification><Order lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:fid="1000952" lims:id="1000952"><Provision lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:fid="1000953" lims:id="1000953" format-ref="indent-0-0" language-align="yes" list-item="no"><Text>His Excellency the Governor General in Council, on the recommendation of the Minister of Transport, pursuant to paragraph 9(1)(c) of the <XRefExternal reference-type="act" link="M-10.01">Motor Vehicle Safety Act</XRefExternal><FootnoteRef idref="footnotea_e">a</FootnoteRef>, hereby makes the annexed <XRefExternal reference-type="regulation" link="SOR-96-446">Nova BUS Corporation Exemption Order</XRefExternal>, being of the opinion that conformity with certain prescribed standards would impede the development of new kinds of buses.</Text><Footnote id="footnotea_e" placement="page" status="official"><Label>a</Label><Text>S.C. 1993, c. 16</Text></Footnote></Provision></Order><Body lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:fid="1000954" lims:id="1000954"><Heading lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:fid="1000955" lims:id="1000955" level="1"><TitleText>Exemption</TitleText></Heading><Section lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:lastAmendedDate="2006-03-22" lims:fid="1000956" lims:id="1000956"><Label>1</Label><Text>Six hundred and fifty units of Nova LFS low-floor model buses, manufactured by Nova BUS Corporation, are exempt from the requirements in subsections 217(11), (14), (17) and (19) of Schedule IV to the <XRefExternal reference-type="regulation" link="C.R.C.,_c._1038">Motor Vehicle Safety Regulations</XRefExternal> that are applicable to push-out windows, for a period of two years beginning on the day on which this Order is registered under the <XRefExternal reference-type="act" link="S-22">Statutory Instruments Act</XRefExternal>.</Text></Section><Heading lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:fid="1000957" lims:id="1000957" level="1"><TitleText>Coming into Force</TitleText></Heading><Section lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:lastAmendedDate="2006-03-22" lims:fid="1000958" lims:id="1000958"><Label>2</Label><Text>This Order comes into force on September 17, 1996.</Text></Section></Body></Regulation>